# Server runtime state — levels, accounts, coins, settings and backups live
# here. These are created and filled in on the server (seeded on first run),
# so we keep them OUT of git on purpose. Durability comes from the
# backups/ folder + the droplet, not from commits.
# It now also holds scrambled passwords and login cookies, so this must
# STAY ignored — never commit data/.
data/
